# Productivity App — Project Overview

Personal daily productivity tracker with ratings (1-5), hierarchical metric groups, weekly/monthly reports, tasks, and notes.

## Context Files (read before starting work)

All project documentation lives in `ai-context/`:

| File | Read when... |
|------|-------------|
| `ai-context/app-concept.md` | Understanding features, rating hierarchy, product decisions |
| `ai-context/project-structure.md` | Creating new files/modules, understanding folder layout |
| `ai-context/tech-stack.md` | Choosing libraries, understanding stack decisions |
| `ai-context/data-model.md` | Working with DB schemas, writing queries, aggregation |
| `ai-context/api-design.md` | Creating/modifying API endpoints, writing HTTP services |
| `ai-context/design-system.md` | Styling, colors, spacing, glass effects, responsive layout |

## Quick Reference

- **Frontend**: Angular 21, standalone components, signals, lazy-loaded routes
- **Backend**: NestJS, Mongoose, JWT auth (Google OAuth)
- **Database**: MongoDB (Atlas)
- **Deploy**: Docker + Railway

## Rules

- All code and UI text in English
- `ai-context/` files can be in Ukrainian — they are not deployed
- Read relevant context files before making changes
- Keep bundle size in check — avoid heavy libraries
